survey_response.review_text: ** ******* ***** ** ******** * ***** ****** *****  ***** it’s becoming harder to find Doctors with human values. Dr. Shriram is an exception in today’s busy world. He is so friendly and explains things very clearly making the patient feel comfortable and mentally strong. His procedural approach in diagnosing the issue makes one comfortable. He doesn’t rush through to attend another patient. Regardless of how many doubts or questions you ask him, he clarifies and responds with a gentle tone and a smile. Definitely recommend this doctor for people suffering with any form of back pain / shoulder pain etc. He is a great asset to the medical field.

Excellent ortho who explains the problem and the solution before advising treatment. The clinic staff are very courteous. X-Ray and physiotherapy are provided at the same clinic for all patients. Highly recommended for all types of ortho related problems irrespective of age.

First of all he gives time to explain about our issues, very patient very expressive about his explanations. And most impressive thing is he does not makes his patients scary. Very positive. I really felt happy to visit him for my elbow discomfort. Thanks for the positivity

Ideal Doctor to consult. He is friendly and makes the patient comfortable. Listened to my complaints fully. Asked for further details, my other health issues and the drugs that I am taking. After examination and x-ray, explained the problem with a knee model. Prescribed drugs taking into consideration my other health problems. Minimum drugs. Prescription is very legible, in capital letters, with clear instructions.
